tweaktrak-wrapper
=================

Wrapper/build automation code in this repository is released under the Unlicense
(see LICENSE).

The TweakTrak web application itself is **not** redistributed from this
repository; it is mirrored from https://tweaktrak.ibiza.dev/ at build time and
packaged into the resulting executables.

Third-party assets bundled into the wrapper
-------------------------------------------

Application icon (musical keyboard, U+1F3B9):
  Source:  Noto Emoji (https://github.com/googlefonts/noto-emoji)
  License: Apache License, Version 2.0
           https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0
  Files:   src-tauri/icons/icon.png
           src-tauri/icons/icon.ico
           electron/build/icon.png
           electron/build/icon.icns
  The PNG glyph from Noto Emoji has been resized into the platform-specific
  icon containers (PNG / ICO / ICNS) used by Tauri and electron-builder. No
  modifications other than resizing have been made to the source artwork.
